 it seems reflection metadata may be necessary for those queried declared classes.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0e0411bc201dcc6b016a0bd9cf162081a38731fb88d2fc5fa3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqC9nis90gn4m1btkxe-P1oYlhiVa9-CawXBXMqTj7JdPXAOqchvJ6xDlqAmG0xqobu086yw3B_UmUHdfs-Or-s9d2vgEqLu8sr3k5l-CxYnTGQX38_cQ3UazHro4g9Qd-z5UuYVw65OTQ0B2nIyyfs2YofYWmzYS0CvOcq-wdKnuclqspm7SNI8mzcogSglFXQarAszNzYKGkhmcL9YcOKQCUSAWSxA7cpq94IP5mddjpG4AZiUIjo9tlKZQsPcCe4e2ttWt7_zQNa7Kh2XPW0xTnxYqy3xWT3ie1S2MCEqQoTclyhbnR7Tp_bjO81lLvYQlRJ3fn73xM2R6Wv659qAthmIL_rIDgSCSkTFrDFwqIi1V36pmPrn_lb2Kcfl8VbJmm6piMcMKic6FVVR8HESCSZDxXxkzOdbqlqK8rXZeW_o868atLFphLM7Q7WYmKmFhzPLtLh23j4Qk3KZCKjeaTIjywvJ5E1zOXSQjNSMvdkRtFSeZ9v_a8GUTIme7bYijRWZP7jU775k9U7nzuoMRP9x9u0TTnmJrn_e_pgCv4O624DVL_ss_p6IlTUIx_P9BXR-re_krziy9K7ejTusId0lum-ZcvR_z-5Qs_n6kNTYeYxFoO2WItaUSnf5ks1v6ZhHihnbAgcfcL1P2JSlr3DLuXcrWPZ8ltMvcghMenUkb9P0AuSfSBcqzg3HCr1fZn1npNK5h4jQEsRpy_VEjS-jF4V_oY4WrzDtcp0sRxraFGgL2NepXoNDQDbYtMan2mJ9YsNLzFGAyu90Apvo1hqd6xdS5zQ2DdwlOqvZUb9RVrUlV86agAuTEvjZnlQJDxAiF8EN9yQ63ftoU0qqGlpVn-zyK_M1LUg3NbiP30t5ejr3yoycGhA7ZjZjtzjVu36bBYzutANWObqZsNlChL2xBvAf2PbgQAbcyCZzHMCyN7SShsT4nFaqwwgEgH5f8_FJ8yuTn7VeRuJT8JDmALwhcehVhbnpNGtUZ7BcakOP-j-r2qhQB-P1bX8Xt5ymTzwDWQnoLXsW_4AhIKrDy85A4ySBtw43K9WVU9OPwJo4Q36ClU_NMbxKek1nsjDsoowIwbTi6IveU1lBTOFAhxSBpYCpQkVov91j-y70n4vf515Ltn_ZVAeYoZAfKUx7h118V0QHsBJm-CP6A9tuqdeQzphgaatffxh4fl8ckHBzv27EJ5u19tQQp5cF3ioP-Dfka9ctCZxP6e8jpzXs7ZEROACX75dodb58eFg5K3wn5TO46_du1-qTJAgXC-uewIZPLnPTv1CXQendufviO3Mv9w6s0Js3bFnKTIzVbPGISFabpiVs0pgkOaDyt2s9U5xx8lELOz6UtGbVNsJsrFXE2LsPIqrxfaB8G6EkCPLXd60ia9FIYoXobW0OhLlcbkHqP3oSdOr3A35gCsOQorUtdQ5pNiEnuD6nLweeCI2nE6A8zoPGoJ1ZpdkJLyDgYvkMiQOUPIuhBs6px2CtiZq66oTRUbV-BbEkf12GBy8Wr7A0bIUyzm_xJ9nGjboDVYgdQg-s2kE8C--UlQ8rxP8o2B0aLd645eO2QxWYflIfpMBAJV0t4ahWkj7vLWj8lbkuxbzPf6GRGrQB-7RbKZWbEn1RByApf_r81vmxlH2VVOoHa04BdULhNHcalE8C83kFUp7ke9Msh4kPeFD-MCF7addLp9bbiXlT3t_0ANPHOjrlc3uvXfqLSJwL4SYjlb6H2lZYEy-xrlsFv8ILcJyer4f9RcVxe5Kxy8qL5i